title: Ep. 26: Face of the NBA, Combine Standouts, Jordan Vs Kobe, and Much More!
description: Our first video podcast! We argue about our all time 5 on 5 teams again. We discuss who will be the future face of the NBA after Lebron James retires. We check in on our sleeper picks, see who made the biggest draft leap, and who the biggest combine surprise was. MJ vs Kobe also was a big topic of discussion.
dc:creator: Griffin Proctor & Joe Jokonya
